# AI-МАТНОРМ Cursor Rules

1. Build the system from scratch using the documents in `/docs` and `/prompts`.
2. Do not import the old MVP as production architecture.
3. Keep backend, frontend, desktop, infra and docs separated.
4. Use typed schemas for all API boundaries.
5. All LLM outputs must be validated against Pydantic/JSON Schema.
6. All long-running jobs must use a job queue and progress events.
7. All calculations must be deterministic and explainable.
8. Every extracted fact must include source evidence.
9. Never store API keys in frontend or logs.
10. Update tests and docs after each implementation step.
